@startuml RAG_Physical_Architecture_Local
!theme plain
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title RAG Physical Architecture - Stage 1: Local Testing

legend right
  **Stage 1: Local Testing**
  All services on one machine (User PC).
  No GPU, no real models. Mock inference only.
  Validate communication links and code logic.
end legend

node "User PC\nWindows / 32GB RAM\n(Development Machine)" as user {
    rectangle "PU-1\nClient Application\n(client/config/local.yaml)" as pu1
    rectangle "PU-2\nRAG Server\n(FastAPI, port 8001)\n(server/config/local.yaml)" as pu2
    rectangle "Milvus Standalone\n(Docker, port 19530)" as milvus
    rectangle "BM25 Index\n(./bm25_data/)" as bm25
    rectangle "PU-3\nInference Worker\n(FastAPI, port 8000)\n(inference/config/local.yaml)\n**MOCK MODE**" as pu3
}

pu1 ..> pu2 : HTTP\n:8001/api/query
pu2 ..> pu3 : HTTP\n:8000/inference/*
pu2 ..> milvus : gRPC\n:19530
pu2 ..> bm25 : local file

note bottom of pu3
  **Mock Mode:**
  - No GPU required
  - No ML models loaded
  - Returns simulated data
  - All endpoints functional
end note

@enduml
